OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FBosses from some of the UK's biggest
OL,8,Fvisitor attractions are gathering for
OL,9,Ftalks with the Met Office aimed at
OL,10,F"fixing" how weather forecasts are
OL,11,Fshown on smartphones.
OL,13,FChester Zoo claims rain icons on
OL,14,Fweather apps can be misleading, saying
OL,15,Fa brief overnight shower can sometimes
OL,16,Fbe shown as an all-day washout.
OL,18,FThat information, it says, can cost
OL,19,Fattractions up to #137,000 in a single
OL,20,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
