OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FIt comes four months after the zoo,
OL,8,Fbacked by more than 80 attractions
OL,9,Fincluding the Eden Project, RHS
OL,10,FGardens, Blackpool Pleasure Beach and
OL,11,FBlenheim Palace, called for changes to
OL,12,Fthe way forecasts are displayed.
OL,14,FOlly Reed, Marketing Director at
OL,15,Ftourism consultancy Navigate, said,
OL,16,F"Our latest data shows this issue
OL,17,Fhasn't gone away, it's become more
OL,18,Fsignificant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,F"In March, we were talking about a 30%
OL,8,Fdrop in visitors from a misleading
OL,9,Frain icon. Today, some attractions are
OL,10,Freporting losses of more than 50%.
OL,12,F"The difference now is that the people
OL,13,Fwho can influence what happens next
OL,14,Fare in the room. That's the point
OL,15,Fwhere a campaign becomes change."
OL,17,FThe zoo says that the Met Office has
OL,18,Fengaged constructively with the
OL,19,Ftourism sector since the campaign
OL,20,Flaunch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FThe event brings together around 30
OL,8,Fdelegates including the head of
OL,9,Fdomestic tourism at the Department for
OL,10,FCulture, Media and Sport and
OL,11,Frepresentatives from the Department
OL,12,Ffor Science, Innovation and Technology.
OL,14,FNew research from Chester Zoo and
OL,15,FNavigate found the majority of UK
OL,16,Fvisitor attractions experience a drop
OL,17,Fin visitors of over 40% following a
OL,18,F"poorly displayed" weather forecast,
OL,19,Fwith some saying they lose more than
OL,20,Fhalf of their customers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FAttractions are proposing that apps
OL,8,Fsplit each day into shorter time slots
OL,9,Fso a brief early-morning shower
OL,10,Fdoesn't skew the picture for the rest
OL,11,Fof the day.
OL,13,FOther suggestions include clearer
OL,14,Fwritten summaries and a "dry hours"
OL,15,Findicator.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FOrganisers say the summit, which
OL,8,Fincludes representatives from
OL,9,FZoological Society of London, the
OL,10,FTreasure Houses Group, Bletchley Park
OL,11,Fand Go Ape, is designed to produce a
OL,12,Fset of jointly agreed recommendations.
OL,14,FDom Strange, Chief Operating Officer
OL,15,Fof Chester Zoo, said, "We've had
OL,16,Fconstructive conversations with the
OL,17,FMet Office, and this summit is the
OL,18,Fnext step.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783939847
OL,3,CZoo hosts summit amid claims poor
OL,4,Cweather app icons cost attractions big
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,F"Getting government and 16 of the
OL,8,Fcountry's biggest attractions round
OL,9,Fthe same table is a real opportunity.
OL,11,F"We want to leave this room with
OL,12,Frecommendations we can actually put
OL,13,Finto practice."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@OO]
